---
summary: Improve documentation of token auth
---
created: 2016-04-18 17:31:48.0
creator: richvdh
description: |-
  https://matrix.org/docs/spec/r0.0.1/client_server.html#token-based is unclear; in particular:

  * several people have confused this token with access tokens and refresh tokens; it would be helpful to spell out that these tokens are a third sort of token.
  * the spec says the token must be a macaroon, but does not clarify what a macaroon is.
