- author: richvdh
  body: |-
    https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-doc/pull/395 removed the compulsory macaroonification

    https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-doc/pull/367 clarified token login.

    Accordingly, I think this is fixed.
